authorizedAccounts(address).notice: Checks whether an account is authorized

buyCollateral(uint256,uint256).notice: Buy collateral from an auction at an increasing discount

getAdjustedBid(uint256,uint256).notice: Get the actual bid that will be used in an auction (taking into account the bidder input)

getApproximateCollateralBought(uint256,u.notice: Calculate how much collateral someone would buy from an auction using the last read redemption price and the old current         discount associated with the auction

getCollateralBought(uint256,uint256).notice: Calculate how much collateral someone would buy from an auction using the latest redemption price fetched from the         OracleRelayer and the latest updated discount associated with the auction

getCollateralFSMAndFinalSystemCoinPrices.notice: Get the collateral price from the FSM and the final system coin price that will be used when bidding in an auction

getCollateralMarketPrice().notice: Fetch the collateral market price (from the oracle, not FSM)

getDiscountedCollateralPrice(uint256,uin.notice: Get the discounted collateral price (using a custom discount)

getFinalBaseCollateralPrice(uint256,uint.notice: Get the collateral price used in bidding by picking between the raw FSM and the oracle market price and taking into account         deviation limits

getNextCurrentDiscount(uint256).notice: Get the upcoming discount that will be used in a specific auction

getSystemCoinCeilingDeviatedPrice(uint25.notice: Get the highest possible price that's at max upperSystemCoinDeviation deviated from the redemption price and at least         minSystemCoinDeviation deviated

getSystemCoinFloorDeviatedPrice(uint256).notice: Get the smallest possible price that's at max lowerSystemCoinDeviation deviated from the redemption price and at least         minSystemCoinDeviation deviated

getSystemCoinMarketPrice().notice: Fetch the system coin market price

modifyParameters(bytes32,bytes).notice: Set a new value for a global specific parameter

modifyParameters(bytes32,bytes32,bytes).notice: Set a new value for a collateral specific parameter

terminateAuctionPrematurely(uint256).notice: Terminate an auction prematurely. Usually called by Global Settlement.
